{"id":"d825be0e-83f7-4de0-8cb5-4cf1751b4331","title":"PPF में कितना interest मिलता है?","messages":[{"id":"1784131863873","role":"user","content":"PPF में कितना interest मिलता है?"},{"id":"1784131863874","role":"assistant","content":"**💡 Quick Answer: PPF पर अभी 7.1% का interest मिलता है।**\n\nPPF (Public Provident Fund) एक बहुत ही popular long-term savings scheme है जो सरकार द्वारा backed है। इसकी सबसे बड़ी खासियत है इसका attractive interest rate और tax benefits।\n\n### PPF Interest Rate Details\n- **वर्तमान ब्याज दर:** 7.1% per annum\n- **ब्याज की गणना:** हर महीने की 5 तारीख से लेकर आखिरी तारीख तक के minimum balance पर ब्याज लगता है\n- **ब्याज का भुगतान:** सालाना होता है, लेकिन हर महीने की गणना होती है\n- **चक्रवृद्धि ब्याज:** सालाना compounding होती है, यानी ब्याज पर भी ब्याज मिलता है\n\n### उदाहरण के लिए\nमान लीजिए आप ₹1 लाख PPF में जमा करते हैं:\n- पहले साल: ₹1 lakh + ₹7,100 (7.1% interest) = ₹1,07,100\n- दूसरे साल: ₹1,07,100 + ₹7,100 + ₹7,597 (7.1% on ₹1,07,100) = ₹1,14,797\n\n### PPF के फायदे\n- **Tax Benefits:** EEE category में आता है, यानी deposit, interest और maturity amount सब tax-free हैं\n- **सुरक्षा:** सरकार द्वारा guaranteed, इसलिए बहुत सुरक्षित है\n- **लंबी अवधि के लिए अच्छा:** 15 साल की lock-in period है, जो अनुशासन बनाए रखने में मदद करती है\n\n### 🎯 Key Takeaway\nPPF एक सुरक्षित और tax-efficient investment option है जो 7.1% का निश्चित return देता है। यह long-term wealth creation के लिए बहुत अच्छा है।\n\n### अगला कदम\n1. PPF account खुलवाने के लिए nearest bank या post office जाएं\n2. हर साल minimum ₹500 जमा करें\n3. MoneyCal के **PPF Calculator** का use करके अपने investment का planning करें: https://moneycal.in/tools/ppf-calculator","isStreaming":false,"sources":[{"title":"EPFO","url":"https://www.epfindia.gov.in/","domain":"epfindia.gov.in"},{"title":"MoneyCal.in","url":"https://moneycal.in","domain":"moneycal.in"}],"recommendations":[{"id":"ppf-calculator","title":"PPF Calculator","description":"Free PPF Calculator India 2025. Calculate PPF maturity, interest earned. ₹500-₹1.5L yearly. 15-50 years. 7.1% rate. EEE tax benefits. SBI, Post Office, banks.","category":"Investment Calculators","url":"/tools/ppf-calculator","keywords":"PPF Calculator Investment Calculators","type":"calculator"},{"id":"compound-interest-calculator","title":"Compound Interest Calculator","description":"Compound interest calculator for investment growth projections with monthly, quarterly, and annual compounding options.","category":"Investment Calculators","url":"/tools/compound-interest-calculator","keywords":"Compound Interest Calculator Investment Calculators","type":"calculator"},{"id":"simple-interest-calculator","title":"Simple Interest Calculator","description":"Simple interest calculator using principal, rate, and tenure to estimate interest amount and total payable or receivable.","category":"Investment Calculators","url":"/tools/simple-interest-calculator","keywords":"Simple Interest Calculator Investment Calculators","type":"calculator"},{"id":"interest-rates-comparison","title":"Interest Rates Comparison","description":"Compare interest rates across banks for various financial products","category":"Banking & Finance Tools","url":"/tools/interest-rates-comparison","keywords":"Interest Rates Comparison Banking & Finance Tools","type":"calculator"}],"followUpQuestions":["PPF में maximum कितना invest कर सकते हैं?","PPF account premature closure कैसे होता है?","PPF और अन्य fixed income investments में क्या अंतर है?"]},{"id":"1784132082082","role":"user","content":"PPF में maximum कितना invest कर सकते हैं?"},{"id":"1784132082083","role":"assistant","content":"**💡 Quick Answer: PPF में maximum ₹1.5 lakh per year invest कर सकते हैं।**\n\nPPF (Public Provident Fund) में investment के कुछ महत्वपूर्ण नियम हैं जो आपको जानने चाहिए:\n\n### PPF Investment Limits\n- **Minimum Investment:** ₹500 per year (चाहे एकमुश्त जमा करें या installments में)\n- **Maximum Investment:** **₹1.5 lakh** per financial year (1 अप्रैल से 31 मार्च तक)\n- **Frequency:** आप एकमुश्त ₹1.5 lakh डाल सकते हैं या छोटे installments में भी deposit कर सकते हैं\n- **Accounts:** एक व्यक्ति केवल एक ही PPF account open करा सकता है (minor के नाम पर अलग account खुलवा सकते हैं)\n\n### कुछ महत्वपूर्ण बातें\n- **Lock-in Period:** 15 साल, लेकिन 5 साल बाद partial withdrawal की सुविधा है\n- **Loan Facility:** 3rd से 6th year के बीच loan लिया जा सकता है (maximum 50% of balance)\n- **Premature Withdrawal:** कुछ conditions के साथ 5 साल बाद withdrawal संभव है\n\n### उदाहरण\nमान लीजिए आप हर महीने ₹12,500 PPF में डालते हैं:\n- Total annual deposit = ₹12,500 × 12 = ₹1.5 lakh (maximum limit)\n- आपको पूरे साल में कभी भी ₹1.5 lakh तक जमा कर सकते हैं, चाहे एक बार में या कई बार में\n\n### PPF के फायदे\n- **Tax Benefits:** Section 80C के तहत ₹1.5 lakh तक tax deduction\n- **Interest पूरी रकम पर:** पूरे balance पर 7.1% interest मिलता है, न कि सिर्फ ₹1.5 lakh पर\n\n### 🎯 Key Takeaway\nPPF में maximum ₹1.5 lakh per year invest कर सकते हैं और यह एक बहुत ही सुरक्षित और tax-efficient investment option है।\n\n### अगला कदम\n1. Check your current PPF contribution और see if you can maximize it to ₹1.5 lakh\n2. MoneyCal के **PPF Calculator** का use करके plan करें: https://moneycal.in/tools/ppf-calculator\n3. अपने PPF account को online manage करने के लिए net banking या mobile banking app का use करें","isStreaming":false,"sources":[{"title":"EPFO","url":"https://www.epfindia.gov.in/","domain":"epfindia.gov.in"},{"title":"MoneyCal.in","url":"https://moneycal.in","domain":"moneycal.in"}],"recommendations":[{"id":"ppf-calculator","title":"PPF Calculator","description":"Free PPF Calculator India 2025. Calculate PPF maturity, interest earned. ₹500-₹1.5L yearly. 15-50 years. 7.1% rate. EEE tax benefits. SBI, Post Office, banks.","category":"Investment Calculators","url":"/tools/ppf-calculator","keywords":"PPF Calculator Investment Calculators","type":"calculator"},{"id":"property-investment-calculator","title":"Property Investment Calculator","description":"Calculate returns on property investments","category":"Property Calculators","url":"/tools/property-investment-calculator","keywords":"Property Investment Calculator Property Calculators","type":"calculator"},{"id":"xirr-tracker","title":"XIRR Tracker for Irregular Investments","description":"Calculate XIRR for irregular investments, SIPs, redemptions, and portfolio cash flows with annualized return tracking.","category":"Investments & Wealth Management","url":"/tools/xirr-tracker","keywords":"XIRR Tracker for Irregular Investments Investments & Wealth Management","type":"calculator"},{"id":"dividend-yield-calculator","title":"Dividend Yield & Reinvestment Calculator","description":"Estimate dividend yield, after-tax dividend income, and long-term corpus impact using reinvestment (DRIP) scenarios.","category":"Investments & Wealth Management","url":"/tools/dividend-yield-calculator","keywords":"Dividend Yield & Reinvestment Calculator Investments & Wealth Management","type":"calculator"}],"followUpQuestions":["PPF से loan कैसे लें?","PPF withdrawal rules क्या हैं?","क्या PPF को joint account में open करा सकते हैं?"]}],"createdAt":"2026-07-15T16:12:04.828Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-15T16:15:42.075Z"}